{"tid":883374,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好攰好辛苦 身邊既人都無哂","createTime":"2018-10-30T19:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T08:41:10.000Z","uid":166948,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e48f8a6fa3b0d6db7c9c6f49dad48e9f9dae7ccb","tid":883374,"uid":166948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T19:44:48.000Z","msg":"利申 final year <br />\n父母好早離婚<br />\n一向無屋企人理<br />\n中三開始晚晚自己食<br />\n <br />\n今年同11年既兄弟反面<br />\n同3年既ex 分手<br />\n呢段日子又變返成日一個人<br />\n係u 有普通fd <br />\n落堂唔見都無兩句<br />\n到最近以為揾到個啱既人<br />\n但feel唔到佢重視我<br />\n平時最鐘意踢波 <br />\n但踢開個隊又無啦啦比人雪 (前幾季都係隊內第一 至第三射手) <br />\n平日返完學成日要去補習<br />\nFinal year又大壓力<br />\n身邊無人陪無人分擔 好攰<br />\n真係好攰<br />\n<br />\n唔會自殺 純粹呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426e5ee5459be2391a0dfeeae77b2b7e34a275a7","tid":883374,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T19:53:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f596b809222956c24cb843272289476506363b90","tid":883374,"uid":206536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知可以同你講到啲咩，但希望你個兄弟會同你和好翻啦，最近我都同你差唔多，感受唔到比人重視，大家一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1238665d80b57796885a092abee00a07e1b62b2","tid":883374,"uid":22012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T19:56:42.000Z","msg":"男人老狗 仲要十一年兄弟 一陣就冇野啦"},{"pid":"1a68431661bd7562cc6058079976a8af2eaf6087","tid":883374,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T23:37:27.000Z","msg":"兄弟搶左你條女？<br />\n11年話反就反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5597fb234b4f2809e714742ab1419e35f9710914","tid":883374,"uid":11285,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T23:40:52.000Z","msg":"眾叛親離有無諗過係自己問題"},{"pid":"fc039652ac3d45e3237378bcb8bbb575afc9a2e4","tid":883374,"uid":166948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5597fb234b4f2809e7147